What you need to know:  Robert Omondi (KDF) proved too strong for Frank Odhiambo (Kibabii University) 27-21 in the U-80kgs division. Elijah Kimani (Regional) defeated Innocent Wafula (Kibabii) 21-20 points in the Over 84kgs division.“The team comprising number one and two from all the categories made the team. They will begin their semi-residential training at the Pipeline taekwondo talent center in two weeks’ time,” said Kenya Taekwondo Federation assistant treasurer Nesmas Wesonga.